title: Bella B Tummy Honey Cream - 4 oz
description: Tummy Honey Cream includes several key ingredients to fade existing stretch marks, including a unique plant extract clinically proven to fade stretch marks typically between 30 to 50%. An emulsion-based formula oil and water that soaks into the skin quickly, it keeps the skin elastic and ultra-moist for several hours. This cream contains no artificial preservatives or parabens, petroleum, or lanolin.
